spec_data.Name: python2-musicbrainzngs
spec_data.Description:
This library implements Python 2 webservice bindings for the
MusicBrainz NGS site, also known as /ws/2.

For more information on the MusicBrainz webservice see:
  http://wiki.musicbrainz.org/XML_Web_Service

spec_data.Summary: Python 2 bindings for MusicBrainz NGS webservice
